{"tid":608094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[復仇者聯盟] 男子侵16歲少女　受害家屬性侵他姐姐報復","createTime":"2018-03-28T01:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T03:41:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6d43cd66f033a267bc9f1ef9e066d6805ef1812b","tid":608094,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:19:50.000Z","msg":"男性侵16歲少女　受害家屬性侵他姐姐報復<br />\n<br />\n16歲的少女被男子性侵，少女的家人為了報復，於是性侵該男子的40歲姐姐。<br />\n<br />\n據巴基斯坦《Geo TV》報導，20日，畢爾馬哈爾(Pir Mahal)的一名男子瓦希姆(Wasim Shehzad)，性侵了一位16歲少女，事件發生後，瓦希姆的家屬希望可以跟受害者和解，於是受害少女的家屬開出了條件，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求瓦希姆40歲的姊姊給他們性侵，最終這個和解內容在21日完成。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當雙方正準備忘記仇恨，要在和解書上簽章時，這起事件就被警方查獲，總共逮捕兩家共12人到案，並進一步追查此起「報復性侵」事件。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"fad66c65ee331326537e2cac1f5d2bfe326fdd46","tid":608094,"uid":170159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好唔爭氣咁笑咗"},{"pid":"e1d45d803429a681361560823be22dec6c6b868a","tid":608094,"uid":10325,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"16 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> vs 40<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3bcbae38a829a460d9e70ddea759528dc665e4","tid":608094,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0172478805a57b94d51965d504e580a82ae226b","tid":608094,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2217be86e45442244527b2ec986fd2781b373d5a","tid":608094,"uid":54524,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"復仇者聯盟<img src=\"/assets/